Dialogs.Dialog: Manaka
This feels good. Should I bring something to play with？
Something to play with... A frisbee or something like that？
I know, I want to play badminton.
Badminton...
What's wrong？
(I can't beat you. I remember this from club activities, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Manaka
There are people walking with their dogs, right？
It's probably the best place for a walk, it's spacious and you can relax. You can come here with your family.
Hmm？
Family... Sounds nice, right？ Hehe！
(It looks you're having fun... What are you thinking？)
Manaka
Rainbow... Ah, over there.
Really... Hmm？ You can see it over there too.
Amazing. Something good might happen, right？
I feel good enough this very moment！
I'm with you... That's how happy I am. I'm kidding.
Manaka
Is this also a power spot？
Power spot？
A place where you can heal and get strength.
Eh？ Then my power spot is――
Next to me？ I'm kidding.
Ah, hey！ It's unfair to say it first！
I got it. Hehe！
Manaka
Hey, shall we go to the shrine？
Okay. I wonder what your wish is.
Isn't it likely that God gets tired of that many wishes？
Then... I'm grateful that you came with me today, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Please make it true▼ I will do the same.
Manaka
Do you know that the God living here is playful？
Playful？
When you make a wish, he whispers at you ear so only you can hear it.
No way！ Okay, let's check it out.
(I wish I can stay together with ▲高嶺＊＊▲！)
That wish will come true.
Huh！？
Hmm？
(It was a hallucination, I hope.)
Manaka
Did you enjoy the movie today？
And you？
It was a jackpot▼ Ah, I want a pamphlet.
Me too. Let's go buy one！
Yes！
How did you like the movie today？
Manaka
I was funny in some way, wasn't it？
I see... I can understand that.
Really？
Yes. Like "let's do our best".
Well, I couldn't really understand Hanamaru. Hehe.
Manaka
Hey, did you understand the story？
No... I'm worried about how to interpret it.
I wonder if reading the pamphlet can help you understand it a little.
I wonder about it... It was a waste to buy it.
That's right... Hmm...
(This movie was such a failure...)
Manaka
How are you？ Have you calmed down？
I'm sorry, I...
It was sad, painful and it repeats. My tears didn't stop.
It was really good...
(I'm glad we come to see it！)
Manaka
I really want to move my body.
Haha, I understand. How about watching this movie？
I want to try to kick like the heroine.
Huh！？
Hey, practice――.
Yes, yes, let's go！
Are you feeling sleepy ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
I got tired from laughing so much.
Haha. I didn't think a movie could make you tired from laughing.
The people who were watching it are definitely laughing, right？
I think laughter will save the world！
It may be. Hehe！
How did you like the movie today？
Manaka
The story was interesting. But...
Even if you explain a fictitious machine that seems to exist, I can't follow it at all...
Certainly.
I think it was science fantasy instead of science fiction .
(...What was that？)
Manaka
Hey, are you okay？
I'm fine. I will heal after you release your grip on me.
But... I gripped quite hard...
It's okay, I'm the one who chose a horror movie！
...Meanie！
Huh？ I'm joking, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！？
Manaka
It was fun.
Did you like it？
Yes▼ The story and characters. I want to see it again...
How about buying a DVD and watch it together？
Yay. Will the DVD come out soon？
The person next to me is a professional.
Manaka
I'm surprised you can recognize someone like that... Would you like to ask him？
Oh, it's unusual for you to tell me that.
Do you want an autograph, or something like that？
I wonder if I can get some lessons. It's better that way, because it takes little time. That's all.
(That's unexpected of you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
I'm so tired！ Let's have a break！
Manaka
Go ahead.
Huh？ What about you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I... Don't worry, just relax okay？
...Why did it become like that？ I'll take a video next time...
(You're so serious, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！)
Manaka
Hey, let's have a match.
...Hoho. Are you trying to challenge me.
Hehe, stop, what's that imitation？ From a manga？
Your confidence is good, come on！
You mean a serious battle, right？ Let's start！
(I think I'm gonna lose！)
Manaka
Wow... It's still beating fast.
Your heart？ Or is it the atmosphere？
Both！ It's like being in an amusement park attraction.
I had a wonderful experience♪
Manaka
The cracking sound was amazing, right？
Right. Wasn't it a mis- adjustment？
I was more interested in that, rather that enjoying it...
Me too. It felt good, but it's a waste...
Yes. Do you think it'll be fixed when we come next time？
Manaka
Ah... Are you okay, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
...I could ask the same, how are you？
Yes, well... Hmm, maybe next time will be different.
That's right. If we don't come together, we won't have fun.
How was today？
Manaka
It was fun. I heard a lot of songs.
I see. Yes.
Hehe, what's wrong？
I'm glad we came here！
I glad to be here with you too. Thank you.
Manaka
My ears are still ringing...
The real pleasure of rock, isn't it？
It's so hot... I wish I could take my clothes off...
What！？
I won't really do it. Geez...
(I was surprised.)
Manaka
Hah...
How was it？
Jazz is not only fun... you can melt with the melodies.
I think we experienced a mature atmosphere today.
Yes... I don't wanna go back home yet.
Emm！？
A joke... I'm kidding.
(Which one is true！？)
It was amazing how they do ad-libs like that.
Manaka
It would be fun if you could play with words like that...
Where did you go？ Don't tell me you have something to do？
Yes, but, it's impossible to think things so fast like that.
Do it！
No. If it was written on paper that would not be as fun...
(I wonder if you can do it someday.)
Manaka
That voice actor is so amazing. He's good at singing.
Right！？ But...
Hmm？
Have you met someone with a voice similar to yours, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Emm, I wonder... I don't know for myself.
(It was similar！)
Manaka
The people who do comedy can draw a lot of stories without difficulty.
Like "It seems like you have a great antenna, every day. I hope catch the news easily."
Should I follow along with a notepad？
Let's create a story and go into the comedy world together！ Like a Manzai couple！
That's wad...
Hmm？
Manaka
There are performances where the audience can join the play. I was surprised.
It was interesting. The amateurs were amazing too.
Even if being put in the stage, they seemed dignified, right？
What about next time？ Your debut as a stage actress, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I'm fine with it. I can't do everything. You know？
(Maybe...)
Manaka
Hey, what is this "history" button？
You can see the history of any played songs, from the person who was here before.
...Is that right？ Then, others can see ours...
That's right. Well then, to show off, let's have a lovey-dovey duet！
...No. "Acorn rolling" please. After that "Sakura sakura" right？
(Does she likes nursery rhymes！？ She's trying to teach me.)
Manaka
...Amazing.
Hmm？ What's wrong？
This menu uses a lot of bread, right？ Plenty of ice cream and honey...
It looks gorgeous, and I think the menu is good here... Want to take a look？
Yes. Ah, no. But...
(I'm worried about her answer...)
Manaka
Hey, can you continue singing？
It's fine... But, aren't I boring you？
You're not boring. Your voice is so nice...
I guess...
So, is it okay？ Please. Let me hear more, please？
(Now, I'm embarrassed！)
Manaka
You can see very far today.
That's my house... impossible.
Where you lived before...？ It would be harder to live there.
Emm？
Ah, sorry. I said something strange, forget it okay？
Manaka
Ah...
Hmm？
No！ Did you saw？
What！？ Wait, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！？
Don't look back there. A couple in the gondola over there is kissing...
(When we are this close, we may be look the same.)
Manaka
Do I have to be a little more scared？
Huh？ Why？
Because... Boys like to protect their girls, right？
Not everyone does. I like your current self, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Emm, geez, suddenly being told that... Okay.
In what kind of haunted house would you be scared in, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
In one where you suddenly disappear like a movie.
(I see... Okay！)
(Okay, just like this...)
Here.
Wow, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Don't play around. It's dangerous.
(Isn't it true...)
Manaka
Ah, hey, are we going in first？
You mean it？ Yay！
I feel like I've gained more confidence.
Let's go "Banzai, banzai！"
Geez, that's dangerous, you know. Hehe, but if it's just a little...
Announcement
We're sorry. Due to strong winds, operations will be suspended.
Manaka
...Does this means it has ended？
We're lucky！ Something like that？
...Is it？ It's a little scary, though the thrill may be double.
...Shall we stop？
Hmm... let's go！
(Sure like challenges ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Manaka
Why do people like this kind of atmosphere？
...In ancient times, fire was sacred. The light that shines in the dark gave hope to humans.
I'm kidding. So？ How was it？
Hehe, didn't you believe it？
Continue with it！
Geez, I'm not doing it.
Manaka
Now, any wish will come true...
We can go now！ We can catch spells！
Time, stop！
...Don't do it. Teehee♪
I wasn't...
Then we have to come again, right？ Until it comes true. Promise.
Manaka
My dream time is almost over...
But even after the parade, we will remain together.
...Yes, the rest of the dream is just with you...
...No, I'm kind of shy.
The slider here seems to be really cool, right？ Right, challenger Takane.
Manaka
What's with that naming. I'm interested, but...
It’s so amazing that my swimsuit has a hole in it.
That's... it's okay！ I will guard you！
...I will stop. I can't be seen by a guard, right？
Wait, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Manaka
There's a couple-only time at the wave pool.
It's an event that seems to be fun. Do you want to go？
Hmm... Just a little...
Hmm...
(She was thinking of the wave pool... I'm curious.)
Manaka
Hey, look. There's a float for two people.
Really. One heart, a community！ Does it feel like that？
That sounds a little interesting. What happens if you push in different directions？
Want to give it a try. Okay, I'll borrow it！
Yes▼
Manaka
I didn't know there was a place where you could see the stars like that.
Eh. Where can we see them？
Alaska. I saw it on TV the other day.
It's too far away！
I have to patiently be here. Someday, I'll take my favorite person there. Right？
(I'll do my best...)
...Hmm？ Huh？
Manaka
...Are you awake？
...Good morning. Were you sleeping？
Yes, deeply. But don't worry... You secrets are safe with me.
What！？ What did I say？
Who knows... I wonder？
(Well, you seem to be in a good mood. What did I say, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
Manaka
...Hey, why did we meet？
Hmm？
Why did it had to be you, in such a wide universe.
I haven't thought about that, but it's obvious.
That's right... maybe？ I can't imagine another possibility.
Manaka
The vitality of plants is amazing, isn't it？
Basically, if you have water and sun light, it seems like you can live.
I wonder... Could I live with only you as my nourishment？
Ah！ It's tasting time！ I'm an all-you-can-eat, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
...Geez. I'm in charge. Wait right there！
(I'm feeling like a dog left behind...)
Manaka
Why are the scientific names of plants so long？
Hmm. That's how... dignity comes out？
Do they make them long so they can sound majestic？
Isn't it necessary for flowers？ Human ego is a good nuisance.
You're just saying things. I will believe you.
(Don't worry about it, be careful not to say anything boring...)
Manaka
Tasting party of edible cactus？
Oh... It seems like it's by reservation. It's a pity.
Does cactus have a texture like aloe？
Ah, maybe it look like it's in yogurt？
I have a small cactus in the garden of my house...
(Hmm？)
Was it fun？ I don't think I have to ask.
Manaka
Why？
I can tell by looking at your face.
I can say the same to you. By your big smile, right？
I was found out. Hah. It's bad！ Fortune come to those who laugh！
It's hard to escape... Don't do it, Geez. Hehe！
Are you having fun, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
I'm with you...
And if you were alone？
Right... I'm sorry for all the people here, but it wouldn't be the same without you.
Then that means I'm so amazing！ Is it okay to interpret it like that？
That's good▼ I'm kidding.
Manaka
Hey, are you okay ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Ah, I'm sorry. I was surprised.
If you got tired, tell me about it, okay？
Hey, let's go there and take a break, right？
(Yes, I'm tired too...)
I didn't sleep today！
Manaka
Don't say it so loud.
Uh, sorry...
Great. But, it was great, right？
There, there▼
(I'm embarrassed...)
Manaka
You were very excited, don't you？
If there is was a fan who only enthusiastically supports me, that would be true.
I wonder if those children also have special people.
Huh！？
What's wrong？ You have a scary face...
(That's taboo, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Manaka
Isn't it hot on the stage.
It must be hot. Especially for musicals.
Singing and dancing, right？ I can't match their strength.
Did you try it, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I can't compete against them.
(Well, that's right...)
Manaka
Want to take a break ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
...I will. Is that okay？
Of course. The forks on your forehead aren't tight enough.
Ah, I'm so sorry！ ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Manaka
Hey, why does that ball fly so much？ It seems to be hard to hit.
It's a flight distance that ignores the laws of home runs.
Hmm... That's right...
...Hey, have you been to the batting center？
(Yes, not it's on fire！)
Manaka
Hah... Wasn't it great？
Haha, it's rare that you get so excited, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
It's because, I wanted to see such beautiful clothes...
That was awesome. It was like a "princess dress".
The prince's clothes were wonderful... I we could wear those clothes and go to the castle...
(It's a maiden's dream...)
Manaka
Ah, can you see it？ The ferris wheel is over there.
Ah, it's true. You can see the ferris wheel.
Yes. I have to confirm it.
Someday we have to try it.
With you, anytime！
Manaka
Ah. Hey, it's shaking.
The bridge shakes a lot...
Isn't this fun？ It's like a trampoline.
Let's jump to make it shake more ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
...Let's do it.
Ah, like this！
Manaka
Without the city lights, the sea is pitch black, right？
I think people in the old days were worried of the sea roar.
But if there is a loved one next to me like this, then...
...That's right.
Hey, your hand... Can we hold hands？
Yes...
Manaka
Hey, what kind of Yakisoba do you think Tropical Yakisoba is？
Tropical Yakisoba？ I wonder if such food is eye-catching. What do you say ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yes, I'm quick-eyed regarding food... Sorry if it's strange.
...I'll go try it.
Safe travels▼
(Why did I speak...！)
Manaka
The sunlight is strong... I may have to apply sunscreen several times today.
If it's to much trouble, I can help you.
Really？
What, is it okay！？
If you make you nose like that, you don't really want to do it, huh？
(I'm sorry...)
Manaka
Ah！？
W-what？
There's something on your face... What's going on？
Ah！ That's sand that got on me while I was sleeping. It's a prank.
There are pranks like that, huh... Hmm...
(I'm thrilled now... ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Manaka
The doggy is doing fine？
It's so crazy how it chases the ball and plays in the sea...
Ah, the ball...
飼い主
I'm sorry！
Oh, come over here！ It's our turn, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Hehe, alright！
Manaka
The wind is a little cold, isn't it？
Want to hold hands？
...No holding.
Huh？
We should join our arms.
Manaka
The stars are amazing...
Do you think they are beautiful because of the cold.
Yes...
Well...
(We need no words right now...)
Manaka
Why does have to be such a flat body.. .
Oh, there is a skeleton diagram.
The more you look at it, the less you will understand...
(I understand why you say that...)
Manaka
That child is following us, right？
I think she might be interested. Who do you think she's most interested in, me or you ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Would you like to give it a try？
This... This one！
The one in the middle？ Hehe▼
(Isn't that cute...)
Manaka
I want to hold the baby penguin.
It's probably fluffy.
I don't have a chance to hold the real thing...
It might not be real, but there are stuffed animals right there. Do you want to go？
Yes, can we go see them？ I can't resist anymore.
(Anymore？)
Manaka
Look, that penguin. It's reacting to light. So cute▼
Somehow, it looks like a fish.
...Ah, maybe. I hadn't thought that way...
I'm sorry, I just said the text...
That's right, the light reflects off the body of the fish...
(Ah, then it's okay...)
...Tonight's dinner is sashimi...
Manaka
...I'm kidding, don't you like it？
Hmm, it's a pity. I really thought you wanted it.
What！ Really？
Just kidding▼
(I was tricked...)
Manaka
Do you know the night aquarium？
Here, at night？
No, another aquarium. I saw it in the news, it's a place where you can stay overnight.
I see. I wish we could do it too.
Hey, I think it would be wonderful to visit.
(Don't discard the "staying" part...)
Manaka
Are the dolphins here born in the aquarium？
I think so. Why？
If you're born in the sea, you might want to return home...
...I see.
I'm sorry, I just said something strange. I wonder why...？
(You're a kind person ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Manaka
It's so crowded...
Alright！ Hold onto my shoulders, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Emm... Me holding you？
Too bad！ That's right！ You holding me, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Ah... Really？ No, stop it, myself...
Manaka
The wind feels damp today.
Ah, it's pouring down！ Dash！
Emm, really？ This is bad！
I'm sorry！ I was joking, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Geez！
(It's bad, I think she's cute being angry...)
There's a sense of openness here.
Manaka
Yes. I want to release my voice.
How？
Emm... Sing aloud？
Sounds good. Now with you, Manaka Takane, number one song this week――.
I won't sing.
Manaka
It would be nice if you could see above the sky.
Above the sky... With a helicopter？ Certainly...
I have to add it to the list "Things to do together one day".
Haha. When did you make it？ There are a lot of things to try.
Please, stay with me until the end▼
Haha, I should ask you the same.
Manaka
Sky Tower's Futah-kun...
It's the mascot here.
Where did "Wao" go？
My little sister called "Wao-chan" will come soon！
Hehe, seems like you're enjoying it！
(...Aren't you enjoying it too？)
Manaka
I want to install a camera here and record a year from morning till night...
I think it can take great photos.
Changes in the four seasons and the changing landscape of the city...
It seems to be difficult to see... I have to fast forward.
One year's worth, right？ Then, does it have more meaning to spend time with you like this？
Of course it does！
Manaka
A crow's singing.
Did you hear its cry？
No. Can you see it？ There's a crow at the bottom.
Ah, it's true. But if doesn't cry, it's invalid.
Emm？
I wont go home until I hear its cry！
That's an understatement. I won't go home too, you know？
Manaka
Wow, a lot of new works.
Haha, it's glittering.
It's shining▼ Isn't it mysterious？ I wasn't interested before.
What a great boyfriend power...
That's how I feel right now！
Manaka
There's a man inside the fitting room...
This is a store for women... Ah, it's unisex.
But it looks a little girly.
That's right.
...Would they look good on you？
(Don't look at me like that！)
Manaka
A beautiful stone...
Which ones. Hmm？ Ah, those earrings.
Does it hurt？ I wonder.
I think it would hurt.
I hate things that hurt... I don't think Papa would approve...
(I see...)
Manaka
Ah, cute hair ornaments. I think it would look good on you.
Huh？
For you▼
...What, for me！？
Look, why don't you try it in front of the mirror？ I'm sure it's cute.
(When she says "cute" it's mysterious...)
Manaka
What are you looking at？ "All-you-can-take with a round massage after washing your face！", huh？
Let's try it...
Stop！
It's no good？ That's fine, though. Why？
(Because it could cause damage...)
Those fake eyelashes are amazing. How do girls do this？
Manaka
A girl can look different with eye make-up... Or so a friend told me.
She emphasized that it was difficult to have those kind of eyelashes as a girl.
Being a male, is it the same feeling as training？
I don't think it's a word that nobody should be happy about...
(Maybe so...)
Manaka
From the shadow of a quiet lakeside forest♪
Cuckoo sings when I'm awake♪
You have to chase it here.
I see. I failed...
But, isn't it amazing it can sing so early？
(Barely, isn't it？)
Manaka
At night, when you look at the sky in the middle of the lake. You can see the stars beautifully.
The light of the city doesn't reach, maybe that's why. But it's little hard to go to the lake at night.
Isn't that dangerous？ I feel a little scared.
That's right... The lake has that kind of atmosphere.
Right... beautiful and likely to be drawn...
(That's a little scary.)
Manaka
Because it's Lake Towano. If so, would I be Tossie？
Tossie... I want some power too！
Then... Tossie！
Haha！ You're very powerful ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Uh... I want to leave it at that. Can we go？
(You are so cute ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Manaka
Emm... it has stopped.
A malfunction？ What do you think we should do？ We might be here for a couple of days.
...If you're here, then it's okay.
I wonder if I'm that reliable...
You're far more than you think... You're great and cool, okay？
Oh, it's fine. Haha！
By the way, are you okay with seasickness, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
I'm okay if it's just this. Compared to a sightseeing, this is nothing.
Then we can go around the world on a cruise！
Will you take me？ Around the world？
...I will work hard.
I'm looking forward to it▼
Manaka
How long does the wake last？
A very long time... Just... Like me and you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
...Is it a good time to give praise now？
Hmm, how was it？ I think it wasn't good.
You're so sloppy. Hehe！
Oh, it's a nice view！
Manaka
Yes. Any tiredness I had is blown away.
Tired tired, fly away！
Can you apply it to anything？
Bento, bento, I wanna eat bento！
Not yet▼
Hah... I'm healed...
Manaka
That's right... I'm kidding.
The air is delicious here... It would be nice to take a nap here.
If you sleep here, won't you surprise the people who's climbing up？？
I should not do it.
Let's do our best. Shall we go？
Maybe it's hard because you use more muscle strength downhill than on uphill.
Manaka
I wonder what would you do if your knees got jerky when going to school.
When that time comes, I'll be your foot, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
...Will you take care of me？
Yes！
At school... I think it would be good here too.
(I think it's not possible on mountain roads.)
I wonder who the chestnuts here belong to.
Manaka
Why？
Because the chestnuts are all over the place. Look.
Really, there are a lot... It belongs to the landlord, right？
However, some people collect wild vegetables, so chestnuts seem to be fine.
...I have to investigate this.
(Your eye color has changed ▲高嶺＊＊▲...！)
Manaka
The red color of the maple is beautiful, but I like the yellow of the ginkgo.
Color？ Because you can get ginkgo, isn't it？
...Isn't it delicious？ Cooked gingko rice.
Oh！ Can you make it？
I won't make it for people who treat others as gluttons.
Manaka
...It's pretty steep...
The advanced course is a bit tough...
...Let's go.
Are you okay？ You really shouldn't over do it, okay？
...I'm sorry. Can I go back？ There's no point in being in such a place.
(I'm glad I didn't show my dislike of losing.)
Manaka
I forgot to apply sunscreen.
I'm going to buy it！
I'm sorry, but it's okay. I know, I'll wrap a handkerchief around my face――
I'm getting suspicious, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Um... May I ask why？
Are you sure that's cute？
Are you really buying it？ Like this？
(Thank you！ I'll go！)
Manaka
That little child is very good.
Truly, he is.
I wonder if adapting is faster when you're young, right？ I'm jealous.
Haha, you're young. High School students are young and we have special training！
We can't lose, right？ Let's work hard, sensei▼
Manaka
It's amazing they can draw pictures that move people's hearts.
Pictures... Are you good at drawing, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Not much... I received an award at school when I was an elementary school student...
Then, it certainly moved people's hearts.
If I hear that kind of compliments, I'll have more confidence.
